  "time_ut": 1661147176,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0da7\u0dda \u0db6\u0dbd\u0dba \u0d9c\u0dad \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dd6\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dc5\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The President reveals a formula that can take power in the country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe made an open invitation to all parties to come to the village and show their work if they want to take power in the country.",
        "The President also said that not only the United National Party, Pohottuwa and Sri Lanka Freedom Party but also other parties are invited to come.",
        "Tell the people of Sajabe to come too. Tell JVP to come too. Let them take a part and cultivate it. If they get twice the yield per acre as we do, they can ask the government to give it. But if you can't do it, it doesn't matter. If power is needed, show that they can work. Come to the village level and do it. The President said in a meeting held in Anuradhapura that he is ready to talk to all parties and bring everyone together."
      ],
